text: Logi Már Einarsson (born 21 August 1964) is an Icelandic politician and architect. He was the Leader of the Social Democratic Alliance from 2016 to 2022. In 2016, he was elected as a member of the Althing. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Icelandic politicians Category:Architects
title: Logi Már Einarsson
